Ds</a><br />\n=====================================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山， 各位修行</span>"},{"pid":"d7027b78970b42cc9c88aa6ff6c158d0d4e65661","tid":1246890,"uid":33938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad3a02364769bb21ab3b9d45be526944d0647ee","tid":1246890,"uid":230730,"like":8,"dislike":86,"score":-78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c0995cba819e28fc369d41b9dfea959e05f64a8","tid":1246890,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:20:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69e7125b00a4a7046c4acfec1e9fcf044c1c3a43","tid":1246890,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7027b78970b42cc9c88aa6ff6c158d0d4e65661","tid":1246890,"uid":33938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱係 講咗幾句就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815e877b0f346924682d3cc32ab9058685d85411","tid":1246890,"uid":80972,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:20:55.000Z","msg":"今日出得黎嘅都係支持反送中嘅中堅分子，始終政府都讓左步，出得黎都係想拎到最完滿嘅公義。<br />\n<br />\n但對住咁嘅龜縮政府，警犬守住個冇人嘅政總，去到金鐘，衝又唔使，和理非又唔係咁做咩好<br />\n<br />\n1) 等齊人，人多好辦事，等到中午過後最多人就可以行動<br />\n<br />\n2) 建立更好嘅溝通方法<br />\n呢場運動贏喺冇大台，最尾都可能輸喺冇大台。去到金鐘，又上唔到連登，班和理非又企得後，一個煙霧彈黎就散哂，。後面冇人，義士就退，警犬就進。今日應該實習一下一個更好嘅溝通<br />\n<br />\n我提議要做<br />\n2a) 建立一個即日清嘅溝通渠道，廣傳俾現場嘅人知。Telegram好，firechat好，有咩入面傾，有決定再出公海。現場嘅人應該對活動有更多主導權，企得後嘅和理非/非義士都知做嘅乜，有事都唔會退得咁快<br />\n<br />\n2b) 建立區域性嘅防守<br />\n雖然冇大台，但我覺得可以有小台，每個區域嘅人應該有合作。講緊嘅係前線後面個d, 比如每個區都揾人清煙霧彈，分左工後面班和理非冇走得咁快。今日得閒可以練習下tim，班速龍成日練先有咁癲，示威者每次都要進步，先會減少失去義士嘅風險<br />\n<br />\n3) 傾下一步要做咩<br />\n<br />\n四點大訴求，set priority ，點樣做，分勇武同和理非傾又好，一齊傾又好，總要傾個方法出黎。<br />\n<br />\n完全撤回《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n收回6月12日「暴動」定性<br />\n撤銷被捕市民檢控<br />\n徹查警察濫權<br />\n<br />\n4) 各有行動<br />\n和理非想做嘅，勇武未必想做，到時咪各自努力囉"},{"pid":"b81f9eb06a044c81c1b2f61eb0218f6c9b57ac48","tid":1246890,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dfce7df4a5847caf17de213a618c7fa80c1520c","tid":1246890,"uid":2612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今次肯定得：我岩岩po左信上美國大媒體Buzzfeed，麻煩入link留comment同share去！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Fhongkongkidsaredying%2Fhong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=3bff19ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個新post（請順便幫我推，我第三晚通頂，跪求可憐我）<br />\n[急！一定有國際傳媒留意] 出左反送中post係國際知名媒體，求大家入link留comment同share<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246617</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[終於有信比大家!] 請廣傳 唔好再比林鄭 黑警 醫管局fake 9外國傳媒，心好累，我連通兩晚頂搵資訊比大家的<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244090</a><br />\n</strong></span></span></blockquote>credit to 月娥奔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b559e9bf60d2c23dc04e2f97c39745783a1b566f","tid":1246890,"uid":33938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"69e7125b00a4a7046c4acfec1e9fcf044c1c3a43","tid":1246890,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7027b78970b42